        {
            "title": "全日收市｜港股收升114點  藥業股跑贏    三指數全周升逾2%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股恒生指數全日升114點，三大指數全周計累升逾2%，全周計藍籌股中快手(01024)升幅最大，石藥(01093)午後飆升，藥業及資源股跑贏大市，晶片股跌，恒指新貴市後正式染藍，收升約1%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：石藥集團官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240527_FI_source-web_01093-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：石藥集團官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240527_FI_source-web_01093-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：石藥集團官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數全日報23792，跌114點或0.48%，今早高開34點或0.14%，報23941點，最高報23951，升45點或0.19%，隨即轉跌，午後跌幅擴大，臨近尾市低見23773，跌133點或0.56%，為全日低點。一周計累升503點或2.16%。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：石藥集團官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240527_FI_source-web_01093-2.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：石藥集團官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240527_FI_source-web_01093-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：石藥集團官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：快手網站\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230703-184037__source-web_快手-图片来源为快手网站kuaishou_source-web__704px.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：快手網站\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230703-184037__source-web_快手-图片来源为快手网站kuaishou_source-web__704px.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：快手網站</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中國宏橋官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20230808_FI_source-web_1378_fb.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中國宏橋官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20230808_FI_source-web_1378_fb.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：中國宏橋官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中芯官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-142318_source-web_00981中芯-2_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-142318_source-web_00981中芯-2_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：中芯官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：石藥集團官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240527_FI_source-web_01093-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：石藥集團官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：快手網站\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230703-184037__source-web_快手-图片来源为快手网站kuaishou_source-web__704px.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：快手網站</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中國宏橋官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20230808_FI_source-web_1378_fb.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：中國宏橋官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-142318_source-web_00981中芯-2_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：中芯官網</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數全日報5286點，跌33點或0.63%，今早開升7點或0.13%，報5327點。科指一周累升2.24%或110點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生國企指數全日報8629，跌54點或0.63%，今早開升6點或0.07%，報8691點。一周累升206點或2.44%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指全日報23723，跌73點或0.31%，低水70點 ; 科指期貨跌45點或0.85%，報5264點，低水23點 ; 國指期貨報8629點，跌37點或0.43%，低水29點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市現成交2356.22億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">總結首周藍籌首三大升幅分別為快手(01024)、石藥(01093)及百威亞太(01876)，全周分別升10.9%、9.4%和6.9%，表現最差首三位藍籌分別是申洲(02313)、攜程(09961)及東方海外(00316)，全周分別挫6.5%、5.5%和5.5%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：快手網站\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230703-184037__source-web_快手-图片来源为快手网站kuaishou_source-web__704px.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：快手網站\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230703-184037__source-web_快手-图片来源为快手网站kuaishou_source-web__704px.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：快手網站</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">藥業股跑贏，石藥(01093)午後突然飆升，全日收升12.72%，報8.86元，為表現最佳藍籌股，成交入20大。滙證上調石藥(01093)評級及目標價，評級升至「買入」，目標價大升1倍，至9.5元。下午02:15出現大手賣出，成交量為240萬，成交價為8.51元，涉資2042萬。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">翰森製藥(03692)升2.84%，報27.2元 ; 中生製藥(01177)升0.44%，報4.55元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">快手(01024)揚8.44%，報59.1億元，據報旗下「可靈AI」，上兩個月月度付費金額均超過1億元人民幣，在推出10個月後(即到今年3月)，年度化收入運行率(ARR)已突破1億美元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">資源股午後向好，中國宏橋(01378)升2.82%，報14.58元 ; 紫金礦業(02899)升2.23%，報18.34元 ; 中國神華(01088)升1.65%，報33.8元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中國宏橋官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20230808_FI_source-web_1378_fb.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中國宏橋官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20230808_FI_source-web_1378_fb.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中國宏橋官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美的(00300)及中通快遞(02057)收市後染藍，美的升1.6%，報76.2元，中通快遞升0.6%，報134.2元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">晶片股弱，中芯(00981)跌4.85%，報40.2元，為表現最差藍籌股 ; 華虹半導體(01347)跌0.94%，報31.7元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中芯官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-142318_source-web_00981中芯-2_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中芯官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-142318_source-web_00981中芯-2_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中芯官網</p>\n</a>\n</div>",
